item.title: How do you fix examines, it keeps on showing .ath
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

  1. This belongs in the Client Help section.
  2. Go to your Client’s Client Class.
  3. Search for the term “Examine”.
  4. Change how it fetches Examines based upon what It’s calling/performing. (I just took out the “Examine” option out for everything in our Client. It looks strange, but It’s better without it in my opinion).
